text: @CuomoPrimeTime @ChrisCuomo I can’t wait to get tested for antibodies for coronavirus. I think I had it, I would love to know, but I already know because I had a hard time taking breaths. I started feeling ill on 3/12, but after thinking about it my nose was running for a week prior.
